@page "/privacy"

<Seo Canonical="/privacy" Title="Blazorise Privacy Policy" Description="At Blazorise, we take your privacy seriously and will only use your personal information to administer your account and provide our services." />

<PageHeader>
    <Title>
        Privacy Policy
    </Title>
    <Description>
        <Paragraph>
            At Blazorise, we take your privacy seriously. This policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal data in connection with our websites, products, and services.
        </Paragraph>
    </Description>
</PageHeader>

<Row>
    <Column Margin="Margin.Is4.FromTop">
        <Container Class="terms-content">
            <Row>
                <Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is8" Margin="Margin.IsAuto.OnX">
                    <OrderedList>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Introduction</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                Blazorise Commercial (“Blazorise”, “we”, “us”) recognizes and respects your right to data confidentiality. We collect, process, and store your personal data in compliance with the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable laws.
                                <br /><br />
                                By continuing to use <Anchor To="https://blazorise.com/" Target="Target.Blank" Title="Link to Blazorise">https://blazorise.com/</Anchor>, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Data We Collect</Strong>
                            <UnorderedList>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>Contact information (name, email, phone number, billing address).</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>Account details (username, license key, product token).</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>Transaction details when purchasing licenses (handled via Paddle).</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>Technical data such as browser type, device information, and cookies.</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                            </UnorderedList>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>How We Use Your Data</Strong>
                            <UnorderedList>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>To provide and manage your account and purchased licenses.</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>To process secure payments through Paddle.</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>To deliver updates, security notices, and support services.</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>To improve our website and user experience (analytics, cookies).</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                                <UnorderedListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>To send optional promotional materials if you consent (you may unsubscribe anytime).</Paragraph>
                                </UnorderedListItem>
                            </UnorderedList>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Purchases & Payments</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                All purchases are handled by <Anchor To="https://paddle.com" Target="Target.Blank" Title="Link to Paddle">Paddle</Anchor>, our authorized reseller and payment processor. Paddle may collect and process personal data such as your name, email, billing address, and payment details to complete transactions.
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                                Paddle is fully compliant with the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and certified to PCI DSS Level 1 standards, ensuring secure handling of payment information.
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                                For more information, please review the <Anchor To="https://www.paddle.com/legal/privacy" Target="Target.Blank" Title="Link to Paddle Privacy Policy">Paddle Privacy Policy</Anchor>.
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                                Blazorise does not store your full payment card details.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Cookies</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                We use cookies to understand user behavior, improve navigation, and remember login details. Cookies are small data files stored on your device.
                                <br /><br />
                                You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Please note, some features may not function properly without cookies.
                                We do not use cookies to access personal data beyond what you provide, nor do we track activity after leaving our website.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>External Links</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any site you visit through external links.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Digital Marketing</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                If you opt-in, we may use your contact information to send newsletters, promotions, and product updates.
                                You can opt out anytime by clicking “unsubscribe” in the email footer or by emailing <Strong>sales@blazorise.com</Strong>.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Data Security</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                We apply appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. Access is limited to employees and partners who require it to perform their duties and are bound by confidentiality obligations.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>GDPR Compliance & Your Rights</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                Under GDPR, you have the right to:
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                                <UnorderedList>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>Access the personal data we hold about you.</UnorderedListItem>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>Request correction of inaccurate data.</UnorderedListItem>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>Request deletion of your data (“right to be forgotten”).</UnorderedListItem>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>Request data portability.</UnorderedListItem>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>Withdraw consent for marketing communications.</UnorderedListItem>
                                </UnorderedList>
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                                To exercise these rights, email <Strong>support@blazorise.com</Strong>. We will respond in a timely manner in accordance with GDPR.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>International Data Transfers</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                If your data is transferred outside the European Economic Area (EEA), we ensure appropriate safeguards (such as Standard Contractual Clauses or equivalent mechanisms) are in place to protect your data.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Data Retention</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide services, comply with legal obligations, or resolve disputes. Account-related data is retained while your account is active. Upon request, we will delete or anonymize your personal data unless retention is legally required.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Changes to This Policy</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page, and where significant, we will notify you via email or account notice.
                                Continued use of the Services after changes become effective constitutes acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                        <OrderedListItem>
                            <Strong>Contact</Strong>
                            <Paragraph>
                                If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us at:
                            </Paragraph>
                            <Paragraph>
                                <UnorderedList Unstyled>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>
                                        <Paragraph>
                                            <Strong>Support Email:</Strong> support@blazorise.com
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </UnorderedListItem>
                                    <UnorderedListItem>
                                        <Paragraph>
                                            <Strong>Sales Inquiries:</Strong> sales@blazorise.com
                                        </Paragraph>
                                    </UnorderedListItem>
                                </UnorderedList>
                            </Paragraph>
                        </OrderedListItem>
                    </OrderedList>
                </Column>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </Column>
</Row>